<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8308667>
    dc:description "FIGURE 52. Species of Squilla Steihn. 1. Squilla maritima (L.) Steinh. from Clusius (1601: 171, as Scilla hispanica); 2. Squilla maritima (L.) Steinh.from Maire (1958: 163, as Urginea maritima); 3. Squilla maritima (L.) Steinh. from Ker Gawler (1806: t. 918, as Ornithogalum squilla); 4. Squilla undulata (Desf.) Mart.-Azorín et al. from Jacquin (1812: pl. 30, as Drimia purpurascens J.Jacq.); 5. Squilla undulata (Desf.) Mart.-Azorín et al. from Desfontaines (1798: t. 88, as Scilla undulata Desf.)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8308667/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8308669>
    dc:description "FIGURE 53. Species of Squilla Steihn. displayed in horizontal rows of images. 1. Squilla hesperia (Webb & Berthel.) Mart.-Azorín et al.; 2. Squilla maritima (L.) Steinh.; 3. Squilla palaestina (M.B.Crespo et al.) Mart.-Azorín et al." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8308669/files/figure.png" ;
