    dc:description "FIGURE 54. Species of Squilla Steinh.displayed in horizontal rows of images. 1. Squilla pancration Steinh.; 2. Squilla serotina (Schousb.) Mart.-Azorín et al.; 3. Squilla undulata (Desf.) Mart.-Azorín et al. (Photograph of leaves by J. Quiles)." ;
